<abstract abstract-type="short" xml:lang="en"><p><![CDATA[Abstract This article is a tribute to the anthropologist Mariza Correa. With the main objective of highlighting her contribution to gender and justice studies, the article also presents her work on the history of anthropology and her efforts towards the institutional construction of this discipline in Brazil.]]></p></abstract>
